OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1774530671
OL,3,CVillage WW1 memorial tree replaced
OL,4,Cafter vandalism over Christmas
OL,6,FA village Christmas tree cut down
OL,7,Fhours after its lights were switched
OL,8,Fon has now been replaced.
OL,10,FThe tree, in Shotton Colliery, County
OL,11,FDurham, had been put up as a monument
OL,12,Fto soldiers who died in the first
OL,13,Fworld war.
OL,15,FStephen Maitland, from the Shotton
OL,16,FResidents Association said he was in
OL,17,F"tears" when he found out that the
OL,18,Ftree - which stood in the village for
OL,19,Fmore than a decade - had been felled
OL,20,Fon 10 December 2025.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
