FL,426,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1774530671
OL,3,CVillage WW1 memorial tree replaced
OL,4,Cafter vandalism over Christmas
OL,6,F"I got a phone call at 10:40pm saying
OL,7,Fthe tree had been cut down and we just
OL,8,Fhad the Christmas tree light up that
OL,9,Fnight. I just couldn't believe what
OL,10,Fhad happened," he said.
OL,12,FVillagers were shocked at the time,
OL,13,Fand support came in from around the
OL,14,Fworld.
OL,16,FMr Maitland added: "It went absolutely
OL,17,Fglobal. There was people texting me
OL,18,Ffrom Australia and other parts of the
OL,19,Fcountry. There was a crowdfunding
OL,20,Fthing set up in Germany.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,426,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1774530671
OL,3,CVillage WW1 memorial tree replaced
OL,4,Cafter vandalism over Christmas
OL,6,F"It wasn't like the Sycamore Gap tree,
OL,7,Fwhere that was a tree that was heavily
OL,8,Fphotographed. This was a monument, and
OL,9,Fit touched everybody in the village."
OL,11,FThe owner of a technology firm donated
OL,12,Fthe new tree, which arrived in Shotton
OL,13,FColliery on 24 March 2026.
OL,15,FMike Adams from Paktech Ltd said: "I
OL,16,Fjust felt it was so gutting coming on
OL,17,Ftop of what happened to Sycamore Gap
OL,18,Ftree, that somebody ought to step in
OL,19,Fand maybe offer to actually replace
OL,20,Fthe tree.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,426,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1774530671
OL,3,CVillage WW1 memorial tree replaced
OL,4,Cafter vandalism over Christmas
OL,6,F"I like Christmas trees anyway and I
OL,7,Fjust think it's a great thing to do
OL,8,Fand I think it's the right thing to do.
OL,10,F"It's a nice tree. I think once it's
OL,11,Fpushed out, give it a couple of years,
OL,12,Fit's going to be impressive.
OL,14,FIt will take some time to reach the
OL,15,Fheights of the previous tree. Theresa
OL,16,FHorn from the Horns Garden Centre told
OL,17,Fus that it's foundations will help it
OL,18,Fflourish.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
