PN,42505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1774530671
OL,3,CVillage WW1 memorial tree replaced
OL,4,Cafter vandalism over Christmas
OL,6,FShe said: "We've backfilled the root
OL,7,Fbowl with tree and shrub compost, and
OL,8,Fthen we've lined it with fish blood
OL,9,Fand bone, which is a slow release
OL,10,Ffertiliser.
OL,12,F"Plenty love and water, we should have
OL,13,Fa good two feet a year on this tree
OL,14,Fafter the first season."
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/5
